descriptionHtml:
Work with us and never run out of Opportunities.

To all the vendors, Here you can work as per your convenience.

Vendor get timely payment.

Vendor get bonus on each service.

Vendor get bonus on each referral.


Features of App -

1. See and accept services on your phone.
2. Get location of customer.
3. Direction of user address on your phone by map.
4. Get earning on your bank account directly by adding bank details .

For more details, please visit our website at https://servicehawk.in

Permission for app and reasons :
Call phone – We use this for calling customer support.
Storage – Use for select profile image from gallery and also upload documents directly from gallery .
Location – We use this for selecting current address of user.
Camera – We use this for take picture for profile and take picture of documents .
